---
title: Beef & Mushroom Ranch Burgers with Bacon plus Herby Potatoes, Mixed Greens & Caesar Dressing
description: Looking for a meal that ticks ALL of the boxes? Found it! Savory beef burger patties are packed with umami-rich ‘shrooms and Parmesan. The burgers are cooked to juicy perfection, then layered onto toasty buns with crisp, smoky bacon, and Monterey Jack. Oh, and did we mention there are oven fries on the side as well as a Caesar-dressed mixed greens salad?  Serve and get ready for the applause!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-mushroom-ranch-burgers-with-bacon-0f4806f8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/beef-mushroom-ranch-burgers-with-bacon-62fba6533234607f410f00a4-0fd6d2e0.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 45 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/beef-and-mushroom-ranch-burgers-with-bacon-62fba6533234607f410f00a4
cuisine: North America
course: main course
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 1630 kcal
